%20happen%20to%20have%20an%20uncle%20in%20Paris%20that%20runs%20and%20operates%20three%20supermarkets%2C%20so%20I%20exactly%20know%20what%20shoplifting%20represents%20for%20retailers%2C%26quot%3B%20cofounder%20Beno%C3%AEt%20Koenig%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVeesion%20said%20its%20tech%20is%20deployed%20in%205%2C000%20stores%20across%20Europe%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20The%20startup%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fveesion.io%2Fen%2Fveesion-secures-e38m-series-b-to-expand-ai-powered-theft-prevention-globally%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20%2443%20million%20Series%20B%20funding%20round%20to%20further%20its%20expansion%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Einto%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20alarm%20over%20shoplifting%20has%20subsided%20somewhat%20over%20the%20past%20year%20as%20retailers%20and%20law%20enforcement%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-depot-shoplifting-retail-theft-challenges-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egotten%20a%20better%20grip%20on%20the%20problem%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Earnings%20call%20mentions%20of%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bshrink%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20industry%20term%20for%20missing%20inventory%2C%20have%20come%20down%20significantly%20among%20the%20major%20retailers%20Business%20Insider%20tracks%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20AlphaSense%2C%20an%20AI%20research%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20though%20shoplifting%20is%20making%20fewer%20headlines%20(especially%20compared%20to%20retail's%20splashy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-target-use-ai-to-prevent-inventory-shortages-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20AI%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20Koenig%20said%20the%20problem%20remains%20a%20compelling%20one%20to%20tackle%20with%20machine%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20glamorous%2C%20but%20the%20ROI%20is%20quite%20direct%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20arrest%20shoplifters%2C%20recover%20inventory%2C%20and%20save%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20difference%20between%20Veesion's%20tech%20and%20some%20other%20visual%20security%20approaches%20is%20that%20it%20says%20it%20doesn't%20rely%20on%20individual%20tracking%20or%20physical%20characteristics%20that%20could%20raise%20concerns%20about%20bias%20or%20personal%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20demo%20image%20of%20a%20person%20concealing%20an%20item%20in%20a%20store%20aisle%20from%20AI%20startup%20Veesion.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852c1e7f748d8c055f3ec56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22842%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20algorithm%20doesn't%20care%20what%20you%20look%20like%2C%20Veesion%20cofounder%20Beno%C3%AEt%20Koenig%20said.%20It%20only%20cares%20what%20you're%20doing.%3Cp%3EVeesion%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20algorithm%20doesn't%20care%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiddle-class-shoplifting-retail-theft-crime-stealing-stores-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhat%20people%20look%20like%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20just%20cares%20about%20how%20your%20body%20parts%20move%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Koenig%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20analyzes%20footage%20from%20the%20existing%20security%20camera%20network%20to%20detect%20humans%20in%20the%20picture%2C%20identify%20their%20movements%2C%20and%20recognize%20various%20objects%2C%20such%20as%20merchandise%2C%20carts%2C%20baskets%2C%20or%20bags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20movement%20is%20deemed%20suspicious%2C%20a%20video%20clip%20is%20flagged%20and%20sent%20to%20store%20security%20personnel%2C%20who%20can%20then%20investigate%20or%20intervene.%20Security%20teams%20can%20update%20the%20app%20with%20additional%20details%20about%20whether%20the%20alert%20was%20necessary%2C%20whether%20a%20theft%20was%20stopped%2C%20or%20how%20much%20a%20stolen%20item%20was%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoenig%20said%20more%20than%2085%25%20of%20alerts%20are%20marked%20as%20relevant%20for%20the%20store%20operators%20using%20the%20Veesion%20system.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHe%20said%20one%20US%20client%20was%20able%20to%20cut%20their%20losses%20from%20the%20health%20and%20beauty%20section%20in%20half%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20of%20implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20US%20retailers%20have%20responded%20to%20the%20shoplifting%20problem%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-walmart-lock-up-underwear-tackle-shoplifting-bay-area-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elocking%20up%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20limiting%20the%20ways%20people%20can%20shop%2C%20but%20that%20approach%20increasingly%20appears%20to%20be%20backfiring%20in%20the%20form%20of%20declining%20sales%20and%20worsening%20customer%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetailers%20have%20implemented%20a%20number%20of%20security%20measures%20%E2%80%94%20many%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20shopping%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20to%20protect%20merchandise%20from%20theft%20and%20to%20keep%20their%20employees%20and%20customers%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20National%20Retail%20Federation%20said%20in%20a%20December%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnrf.com%2Fresearch%2Fthe-impact-of-retail-theft-violence-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20retail%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20layering%20onto%20a%20store's%20existing%20security%20camera%20infrastructure%20and%20alerting%20staff%20to%20specific%20risky%20behavior%2C%20Veesion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fveesion.io%2Fen%2Fis-your-security-helping-or-hurting-your-cx%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20tech%20can%20help%20create%20a%20more%20pleasant%20shopping%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22350%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20demo%20of%20the%20security%20alert%20scree