0Eric%20Gonzalez%2C%20a%20neuroscience%20professor%20at%20Texas%20Christian%20University%20who%20has%20studied%20creatine%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anyone%20wants%20to%20go%20on%20a%20supplement%2C%20creatine%20won't%20hurt%20you%2C%20there's%20only%20going%20to%20be%20an%20upside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20losing%20weight%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20on%20a%20GLP-1%20drug%20that%20triggers%20weight%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20creatine%20can%20help%20you%20retain%20muscle%20mass%2C%20promoting%20a%20higher%20ratio%20of%20muscle%20to%20body%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-ways-to-improve-your-mood-according-to-psychologists%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboost%20brain%20health%20or%20mood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20early%20studies%20suggest%20that%2010-30%20grams%20a%20day%20may%20be%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlen%20previously%20conducted%20research%20on%20senior%20Olympians%20who%20took%20creatine%20and%20found%20it%20helped%20them%20get%20stronger%20and%20faster%20while%20avoiding%20age-related%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20never%20too%20old%20to%20take%20creatine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-demand-soars-muscle-fat-loss-and-brain-power-benefits-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750499101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685568cbf748d8c055f40bba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreatine-demand-soars-muscle-fat-loss-and-brain-power-benefits-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Creatine%2C%20beyond%20its%20muscle-building%20qualities%2C%20aids%20in%20fat%20loss%2C%20cognitive%20longevity%2C%20and%20heart%20health%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sales%20are%20booming.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%2