20showdown%20in%20front%20of%20a%20child.%20Somehow%2C%20I%20always%20end%20up%20with%20the%20mystery%20leftovers%2C%20maybe%20because%20I'm%20the%20only%20one%20who%20doesn't%20gag%20at%20the%20sight%20(or%20smell)%20of%20week-old%20pasta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20moved%20in%20together%2C%20my%20ex%20and%20I%20weren't%20exactly%20best%20friends%2C%20but%20we'd%20found%20a%20respectful%20rhythm%20texting%20about%20our%20kid%2C%20showing%20up%20for%20day%20care%20pickups%2C%20and%20just%20generally%20keeping%20things%20polite.%20Co-habiting%20felt%20daunting%2C%20but%20necessary.%20And%20gradually%2C%20we%20figured%20it%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20everything's%20on%20the%20table%2C%20literally%20and%20emotionally.%20We%20created%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshared-google-calendar-key-successful-marriage-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20calendar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20divide%20up%20pickups%2C%20grocery%20runs%2C%20and%20chores.%20Mondays%20and%20Thursdays%20are%20my%20dish%20days.%20He%20takes%20out%20the%20trash%20and%20does%20the%20laundry.%20Our%20third%20housemate%20covers%20groceries%20and%20makes%20lunches%20for%20our%20kid.%20When%20conflicts%20pop%20up%20(and%20they%20do)%2C%20we%20have%20a%20rule%3A%20no%20letting%20things%20fester.%20We%20talk%20it%20out%20on%20%26quot%3Bporch%20check-ins%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20weekly%2020-minute%20chat%20outside%2C%20away%20from%20our%20daughter%2C%20just%20to%20vent%20or%20recalibrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20like%20running%20a%20tiny%20domestic%20government%2C%20but%20the%20policies%20revolve%20around%20nap%20schedules%20and%20snack%20preferences%20instead%20of%20tax%20codes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d32c225a-e423-4554-9b76-cadd826d2299%5C%22%3ELiving%20together%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20easier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20growing%20pains%2C%20living%20together%20like%20this%20has%20its%20perks.%20Three%20adults%20mean%20there's%20always