d%20gets%20it.%20She's%205%2C%20and%20she%20knows%20the%20rhythm%20of%20three%20nights%20with%20me%2C%20three%20with%20her%20dad%2C%20one%20shared%20dinner%20all%20together.%20We%20don't%20trade%20off%20in%20parking%20lots%3B%20we%20live%20in%20the%20same%20apartment%2C%20just%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgirlfriend-boyfriend-living-together-have-separate-bedrooms-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseparate%20rooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20toys%20stay%20put%2C%20her%20bedtime%20routine%20doesn't%20change%2C%20and%20if%20she%20forgets%20something%2C%20it's%20just%20down%20the%20hall.%20It's%20not%20perfect%2C%20but%20it's%20peaceful%2C%20and%20she%20never%20feels%20like%20she's%20being%20split%20in%20two.%20The%20other%20day%2C%20she%20proudly%20told%20a%20friend%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20family's%20weird%2C%20but%20it's%20cool.%26quot%3B%20That%20felt%20like%20the%20ultimate%20seal%20of%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20with%20my%20ex%20and%20his%20wife%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20co-parenting%20isn't%20a%20competition.%20It's%20a%20collaboration.%20It's%20messy%2C%20funny%2C%20and%20full%20of%20poop%20emojis%2C%20but%20it%20works.%20And%20honestly%2C%20isn't%20that%20what%20parenting%20is%20all%20about%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20no%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20cult%20or%20a%20sitcom.%20It's%20just%20modern%20life.%20Three%20adults%2C%20one%205-year-old%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20love%2C%20laughter%2C%20and%20compromises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-with-ex-wife-coparent-kid-save-money-rent-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750497662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6852c9b2f748d8c055f3edad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-with-ex-wife-coparent-kid-save-money-rent-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20live%20with%20my%20e