%20I've%20always%20kept%20my%20eye%20on%20Virgin%20Limited%20Edition%20because%20it%20felt%20more%20my%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20lived%20abroad%20before%20working%20as%20a%20cast%20member%20for%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida%20for%20seven%20years%20after%20university%2C%20but%20I'd%20never%20lived%20on%20an%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20the%20head%20of%20guest%20services%20role%2C%20and%20I%20sent%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20They%20invited%20me%20for%20an%20interview%2C%20and%20I%20made%20it%20to%20the%20final%20stage.%20I%20told%20my%20husband%20we%20might%20have%20to%20move%2C%20and%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAlright.%20Let's%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d2374dd-bd7d-4901-ba83-56b3d60c3486%5C%22%3EWe%20didn't%20know%20much%20about%20Richard%20Branson's%20island%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20heard%20Necker%20Island%20was%20incredible%2C%20but%20apart%20from%20that%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20preconceptions.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20applied%20for%20our%20visas%20and%20went%20for%20it%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20always%20been%20adventurous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20arrived%20by%20boat%20in%20April%202022.%20We'd%20moved%20our%20whole%20lives%20to%20this%20tiny%20island%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0it%20was%20amazing%20and%20nerve-racking.%20I%20remember%20going%20to%20the%20staff%20village%20and%20being%20greeted%20by%20my%20new%20co-workers%20who%20were%20having%20a%20party.%20The%20next%20morning%2C%20I%20could%20see%20Necker%20Island%20properly.%20It's%20total%20paradise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2024%20rooms%20on%20the%20island%2C%20spread%20across%20the%20%26quot%3BGreat%20House%26quot%3B%20and%20individual%20Balinese%20houses%20around%20the%20island.%20Necker%20also%20has%20two%20private%20beaches.%20Our%20conservation%20team%20looks%20after%20the%20island's%20giant%20tortoises%20and%20lemurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20guest%20room%20on%20Necker%20Island%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685574983d5881a51c1bc5c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20guest%20room%20on%20Necker%20Island%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Limited%20Editions%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGuests%20can%20book%20the%20island%20exclusively%20or%20non-exclusively%20with%20other%20guests%20from%20June%20to%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20typical%20guest.%20People%20will%20come%20to%20Necker%20Island%20for%20a%20conference%20or%20to%20celebrate%20a%20birthday%2C%20and%20Richard%20brings%20a%20lot%20of%20philanthropic%20groups.%20We%20keep%20the%20identity%20of%20our%20guests%20close%20to%20our%20chests%2C%20but%20I've%20met%20people%20that%20I%20never%20would%20have%20expected%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f5959b7-8b55-446e-ad5d-99291119adbc%5C%22%3EMy%20day-to-day%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20responsibilities%20range%20from%20running%20logistics%20with%20the%20boat%20team%20to%20picking%20up%20guests%2C%20to%20chatting%20with%20engineers%20about%20the%20wind%20turbines%2C%20to%20helping%20housekeepers%20take%20linen%20off%20the%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20I'll%20go%20to%20the%20Great%20House%20and%20chat%20to%20the%20guests%20having%20breakfast%20about%20their%20evening.%20We%20will%20have%20a%20team%20briefing%20and%20go%20through%20the%20guests'%20plans%20for%20the%20day.%20A%20day%20could%20include%20kangaroo%20yoga%2C%20a%20lemur%20feed%2C%20lunch%20in%20Turtle%20Beach%2C%20and%20tennis%20in%20the%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227815%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Master%20suite%20in%20the%20Great%20House%20on%20Necker%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F685574983d5881a51c1bc5c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMaster%20suite%20in%20the%20Great%20House%20on%20Necker%20Island.%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Limited%20Editions%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20work%209-to-5%2C%20and%20sometimes%20I'm%20partying%20with%20the%20guests%20until%204%20a.m.%20After%20work%2C%20we%20can%20go%20to%20the%20beach%20for%20sunset%2C%20but%20sometimes%20we'll%20put%20on%20Netflix.%20Other%20nights%20we'll%20leave%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20Necker%20staff%20are%20local%20and%20live%20on%20Tortola%20or%20our%20neighbouring%20island%2C%20Virgin%20Gorda.%20We%20also%20have%20an%20employee%20village%20on%20Necker%20Island.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20BVI%20is%20surprisingly%20comparable%20to%20living%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0898202-8a13-4a8c-882e-4b867379e170%5C%22%3EThe%20island%20is%20paradise%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20hard%20days%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20downtime%2C%20staff%20can%20use%20the%20island's%20amenities%20and%20go%20kite%20surfing%2C%20use%20the%20tennis%20courts%2C%20or%20go%20scuba%20diving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20places%20on%20the%20island%20is%20the%20crow's%20nest%3A%20a%20hot%20tub%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20the%20Great%20House.%20I%20like%20watching%20the%20stars%20there%20because%20there's%20not%20much%20light%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226620%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Great%20House%20pool%20on%20Necker%20Island%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68557498f748d8c055f40dab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224413%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Great%20House%20pool%20on%20Necker%20Island.%3Cp%3EVirgin%20Limited%20Editions%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Richard%20Branson%20and%20his%20wife%20Joan%20aren't%20traveling%2C%20the%20island%20is%20their%20home%2C%20and%20we%20see%20them%20often.%20They%20are%20generous%20and%20kind%2C%20and%20often%20invite%20us%20to%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20challenging%20days%2C%20like%20when%20Hurricane%20Ernesto%20came%20through%20in%202