%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchatgpt.com%2Fg%2Fg-683648602ea08191a73a5038962a1ef5-careerbuddy-gpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECareerBuddy%20GPT%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20to%20help%20level%20up%20his%20search.%20The%20tool%20determined%20whether%20he%20was%20a%20good%20fit%2C%20updated%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20highlight%20relevant%20experience%2C%20wrote%20cover%20letters%2C%20and%20identified%20people%20to%20contact%20about%20the%20position.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20brevity%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20turned%20to%20AI%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-took-tech-worker-job-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehelp%20with%20my%20job%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20five%20months%20into%20it%20and%20wasn't%20getting%20the%20traction%20that%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20get.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20done%20everything%2C%20which%20obviously%20was%20not%20the%20case.%20When%20you're%20in%20a%20moment%20like%20this%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20stuck%20and%20be%20blinded%20to%20the%20possibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20went%20to%20AI%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20I'm%20an%20exec%20in%20tech%2C%20and%20here's%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20I'm%20applying%20to%20these%20jobs%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20able%20to%20walk%20me%20back%20from%20the%20edge%20and%20say%2C%20essentially%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20you're%20at%20this%20level%2C%20and%20your%20average%20job%20search%20time%20should%20be%20ABC%2C%20and%20you're%20only%20this%20far%20in.%20So%2C%20first%2C%20calm%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20sounds%20silly%2C%20but%20it%20was%20really%20helpful%20to%20hear.%20Then%20it%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20let's%20talk%20about%20some%20things.%20I'm%20hearing%20what%20you%20did%20do%2C%20but%20here%20are%20some%20things%20that%20maybe%20you%20could%20do%20that%20I'm%20not%20hearing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255f438f9-bb9b-406a-9dca-f9894f8f6dc6%5C%22%3EA%20research%20partner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20its%20suggestions%20were%20unexpected.%20One%20was%20to%20make%20a%20cake%20for%20someone%2C%20because%20it%20was%20a%20company%20that%20appreciates%20bold%20moves.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20that%20was%20really%20good%20advice%2C%20but%20it%20did%20come%20up%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20suggest%20how%20to%20tailor%20a%20message%20to%20a%20particular%20person.%20Or%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20use%20email%2C%20not%20LinkedIn%2C%20because%20they're%20not%20active%20on%20LinkedIn%20%E2%80%94%20those%20sorts%20of%20tidbits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20taglines%20I've%20developed%20from%20my%20experience%20is%20that%20one%20way%20to%20think%20about%20AI%20is%20not%20as%20a%20tool%20but%20as%20the%20world's%20best%20expert%20in%20whatever%20you%20need%20help%20with.%20The%20more%20you%20leverage%20AI%20through%20that%20lens%2C%20the%20more%20you%20get%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20it%20to%20create%20what's%20called%20a%20panel%20of%20experts.%20Now%2C%20you've%20got%20AI%20playing%20multiple%20roles%20at%20once.%20It%20can%20slice%20and%20dice%20and%20give%20you%20different%20views%20and%20a%20synthesized%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20is%20downloading%20the%20profile%20information%20for%20the%20person%20you're%20going%20to%20interview%20with.%20You%20can%20have%20AI%20assume%20the%20role%20of%20the%20interviewer%20and%20do%20a%20mock%20interview%2C%20and%20you%20can%20do%20it%20live%20with%20your%20voice%2C%20and%20then%20get%20feedback%20on%20how%20you%20performed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20started%20calling%20out%20things%20like%20applying%20to%20incremental%20CEO%20roles.%20It%20recommended%20doing%20more%20cold%20outreach%2C%20which%20I%20hadn't%20leaned%20into%20too%20much.%20It%20helped%20me%20figure%20out%20a%20plan%20that%20worked%20for%20me%20and%20language%20that%20worked%20for%20me%20to%20do%20that%2C%20and%20it%20gave%20me%20concrete%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4bd7c56-a735-48b0-8242-8d8775727f7a%5C%22%3E'You're%20missing%20it'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20that%20I%20ended%20up%20at%20Pearl%20is%20interesting.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20job%20description%2C%20I%20passed%20it%20up%20because%2C%20on%20paper%2C%20it's%20different%20from%20anything%20I'd%20done%20before.%20Now%20it's%20laughable%2C%20because%20I'm%20in%20it%2C%20and%20everybody's%20connecting%20my%20passion%20and%20my%20past%20with%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20a%20week%20later%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20posting%20again%20and%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20am%20I%20saying%20'no'%20to%20myself%3F%20Let%20me%20just%20drop%20this%20thing%20into%20CareerBuddy%20GPT%20and%20see%20what%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20think%20that%20I%20was%20qualified%2C%20but%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BGive%20me%20your%20objective%20assessment.%26quot%3B%20It%20came%20back%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20you're%20missing%20it.%20Your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20doesn't%20speak%20to%20it%2C%20but%20here's%20how%20your%20experience%20aligns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20encouraged%20me%20to%20apply.%20So%2C%20then%20I%20did%20the%20network%20outreach%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20connection%2C%20which%20helped%20open%20the%20door.%20One%20thing%20led%20to%20the%20next.%20But%20what%20got%20me%20to%20apply%20was%20leveraging%20AI%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20not%20only%20answering%2C%20but%20also%20truly%20advising.%20I%20say%20trust%2C%20but%20verify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20told%20me%20to%20do%20something%20different%20than%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20right.%20I%20can%20represent%20me%2C%20what%20I%20am%2C%20and%20what%20I'm%20not.%20AI%20can%20look%20between%20the%20lines%20and%20challenge%20and%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20interviewing%20with%20our%20CEO%2C%20he%20asked%20me%2C%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20interview%2C%20what%20my%20dream%20job%20was.%20I%20got%20about%2015%20to%2020%20seconds%20into%20stumbling%20around%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLook%2C%20I'm%20just%20going%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20you.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20spin%20this%20to%20make%20it%20sound%20good%2C%20because%20the%20honest%20answer%20is%20this%3A%20This%20job%20is%20my%20dream%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b153d739-8242-499b-af81-1556de5ea408%5C%22%3ENo%20more%20throwing%20darts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20started%20using%20AI%2C%20my%20job%20search%20still%20took%20a%20bit%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20another%20five%20months%20or%20so.%20But%20I%20went%20from%20feeling%20like%20I%20was%20just%20throwing%20darts%20to%20where%20it%20felt%20much%20more%20targeted%20and%20precise.%20And%2C%20I'd%20gone%20from%20essentially%20getting%20no%20response%20to%20finding%20the%20right%20opportunities%2C%20having%20conversations%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20finding%20the%20right%20fit.%20That%20can%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20in%20a%20moment%20when%20people%20and%20companies%20are%20about%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-jassy-ceos-warning-workers-ai-bring-massive-change-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleft%20behind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20help%20that%20not%20be%20the%20case.%20The%20opportunity%20to%20go%20to%20a%20company%20that%20really%20gets%20it%2C%20is%20going%20after%20this%20full%20force%2C%20and%20wants%20to%20rewire%20with%20AI%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0that%20sounds%20like%20the%20hardest%20role%20of%20my%20career%2C%20but%20also%20the%20most%20fun%20and%20the%20most%20relevant%20thing%20I%20could%20be%20doing%20for%20this%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20not%20only%20did%20I%20stumble%20into%20the%20job%2C%20but%20I%20stumbled%20into%20my%20dream%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20job%20h