%3EJust%20like%20the%20snail%20delicacy%2C%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20Kudal%20Varuval%20(Goat%20intestines)%20has%20pleasantly%20surprised%20the%20chef.%20Most%20big%20restaurants%20in%20cities%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20itself%20don%E2%80%99t%20serve%20intestines%2C%20says%20chef%20Vijaya%2C%20which%20he%20recalls%20was%20given%20away%20free%20at%20the%20butcher%20shop%20in%20his%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoing%20beyond%20Chicken%20Tikka%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Semma%20and%20Unapologetic%20Foods%2C%20what%20Roni%20and%20the%20team%20aim%20for%20is%20to%20share%20their%20stories.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20big%20barrier%20and%20preconceived%20notion%20about%20how%20we%20look%20at%20food.%20We%20only%20look%20at%20it%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20economics.%20In%20this%20process%2C%20we%20eliminated%20certain%20foods%20from%20our%20conversation.%20We%20believe%20that%20flavour%20should%20not%20be%20bound%20by%20economics.%20We%20will%20not%20hold%20back%2C%20our%20food%20will%20have%20real%20spices.%20We%20will%20not%20serve%20boneless%20and%20fillet%20versions%20of%20our%20dishes.%20By%20doing%20that%2C%20you%20are%20eliminating%20the%20real%20cultural%20context%20of%20the%20dish%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2Fezgif-5-214f0439b2-min-1665581139-500x443.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chettinad%20Maan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2Fezgif-5-214f0439b2-min-1665581139-500x443.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2Fezgif-5-214f0439b2-min-1665581139-300x266.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2Fezgif-5-214f