s%20always%20a%20samosa%20sold%20in%20a%20South%20Indian%20restaurant%20which%20serves%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Echicken%20tikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Mughlai%2FPunjabi%20food%20is%20being%20sold%20as%20%E2%80%98Indian%20food%E2%80%99.%20But%20we%20are%20so%20much%20more%20than%20that.%20There%20is%20Tamilian%2C%20Bengali%2C%20Gujarati%2C%20Punjabi%2C%20and%20Marathi%20cuisine%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20So%20in%20our%20restaurant%2C%20there%20is%20no%20middle%20ground%2C%20and%20we%E2%80%99re%20proud%20of%20it.%20We%20have%20unshackled%20ourselves%20from%20that%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roni%20says%20with%20a%20grin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20there%20is%20no%20basmati%20rice%2C%20samosa%2C%20naan%20or%20chicken%20tikka%20masala%20at%20Semma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUntitled-design-2022-10-12T185924.978-1665581378.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team%20behind%20Semma%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUntitled-design-2022-10-12T185924.978-1665581378.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUntitled-design-2022-10-12T185924.978-1665581378-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUntitled-design-2022-10-12T185924.978-1665581378-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUntitled-design-2022-10-12T185924.978-1665581378-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FUntitled-design-2022-10-12T185924.978-1665581378-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-299911%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%20behind%20Semma-%20Chintan%20Pandya%2C%20Vijaya%20Kumar%20and%20Roni%20Mazumdar.%20Image%3A%20Paul%20McDonough%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dishes%20are%20given%20their%20true%20South%20Indian%20names%20sans%20English%20translations.%20Chef%20Vijaya%20says%20that%20if%20mushrooms%20can%20be%20called%20%3Cem%3Efunghi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20an%20Italian%20restaurant%2C%20why%20should%20%3Cem%3Ekozhi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebe%20called%20%E2%80%98chicken%E2%80%99%20on%20their%20menu%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Roni%20credits%20the%20chef%20for%20the%20restaurant%E2%80%99s%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20success%20of%20Semma%20is%20Vijay%E2%80%99s%20vulnerability.%20You%20truly%20get%20the%20chef%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20in%20his%20food.%20He%20has%20bared%20his%20soul.%20It%20is%20because%20he%20has%20owned%20who%20he%20is.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20liberating.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20fit%20into%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20love%20and%20feedback%20of%20people%20keep%20this%20team%20going.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20old%20gentleman%20just%20sitting%20alone%20at%20the%20table.%20I%20asked%20him%20if%20everything%20was%20okay.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20was%20remembering%20his%20grandfather.%20The%20food%20he%20ate%20reminded%20him%20of%20eating%20at%20his%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20house%2C%20and%20he%20said%20that%20since%20he%20left%20Chennai%20many%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20never%20eaten%20anything%20like%20it.%20People%20have%20shed%20tears%20after%20eating%20the%20food%20as%20they%20remember%20moments%20from%20their%20childhood.%20They%20connect%20with%20us%20on%20a%20human%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Roni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20no%20longer%20bend%20to%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20rules%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20empowering%20to%20everyone%20around%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Yoshita%20Rao%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EImages%20by%20Paul%20McDonough%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750430161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2FCopy-of-Nathai-Pirattal-snails-photo-credit-Paul-McDonough-min-1665580840.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D452925%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Semma%E2%80%99s%20chef%20brings%20childhood%20memories%20and%20bold%20regional%20flavours%20to%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20earning%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20honours%20in%20the%20culinary%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F452925%2Fchef-vijaya-kumar-james-beard-award-semma%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM-Kisan%2020th%20Instalment%3A%20How%20Farmers%20Can%20Register%20%26amp%3B%20Complete%20e-KYC%20to%20Get%20Rs%202%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%2011%20crore%20farmers%20in%20India%20benefit%20from%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmkisan.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20PM-Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20receiving%20Rs%202%2C000%20every%20few%20months%20directly%20into%20their%20bank%20accounts.%20However%2C%20to%20continue%20receiving%20these%20funds%E2%80%94especially%20for%20the%20upcoming%2020th%20instalment%20%E2%80%94%20farmers%20must%20complete%20a%20mandatory%20e-KYC%20before%20the%20June%2030%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20fund%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F451384%2Fsustainable-farming-methods-for-farmers-to-adopt-this-kharif-monsoon-season%2F%5C%22%20target%3D