%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%20300%20sunny%20days%20a%20year%2C%20Ladakh%20is%20poised%20to%20transform%20its%20extreme%20climate%20into%20its%20greatest%20energy%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brilliant%20example%20of%20this%20potential%20in%20action%20can%20be%20found%20at%20the%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20(ITBP)%20campus%20in%20Leh.%20Here%2C%20a%20smart%20and%20sustainable%20solar%20setup%20is%20helping%20two%20massive%20four-storey%20buildings%20stay%20warm%20without%20burning%20a%20single%20drop%20of%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%3F%20Through%20an%20innovative%20Concentrated%20Solar%20Power%20(CSP)%20system%20that%20captures%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20rays%20and%20converts%20them%20into%20indoor%20warmth.%20Think%20of%20it%20like%20this%3A%20curved%20mirrors%20focus%20sunlight%20onto%20a%20silver%20tray%2C%20heating%20glycol-water%20solution%20to%20around%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%2050%20degrees%20Celsius.%20This%20hot%20solution%20flows%20beneath%20the%20floors%20of%20the%20buildings%2C%20gently%20warming%20the%20rooms%20to%20a%20cozy%2015%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%2020%20degrees%20Celsius%20even%20when%20it%20is%20as%20freezing%20as%20-30%20degrees%20Celsius%20outside!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20staying%20warm.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20shining%20example%20(literally!)%20of%20how%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20intense%20sunlight%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20a%20clean%2C%20efficient%20and%20eco-friendly%20solution%20for%20extreme%20climates.%20Who%20says%20the%20cold%20desert%20can%E2%80%99t%20lead%20India%E2%80%99s%20renewable%20energy%20story%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20solar%20potential%20like%20no%20other%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20yo