%20over%20how%20we%20grow%20and%20who%20we%20serve.%20Initially%2C%20when%20I%20was%20in%20the%20last%20year%20of%20graduation%2C%20I%20started%20collecting%20the%20scrap%20with%20pocket%20money%2C%20then%20as%20the%20business%20grew%2C%20we%20started%20earning%20money%20from%20it%20and%20reinvested%20it%20in%20the%20business.%20We%20have%20never%20burned%20any%20cash%20to%20sustain%20this%20business%2C%20and%20from%20day%20one%2C%20we%20have%20been%20profitable%20at%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20is%20to%20build%20a%20business%20that%20can%20save%20our%20Earth%20from%20becoming%20a%20dumping%20ground%20and%20which%20will%20be%20financially%20stable%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Scrapdeal%20directly%20employs%2030%20people%20and%20supports%20the%20livelihood%20of%20over%20200%20others%20indirectly%2C%20including%20waste%20collectors%2C%20transporters%2C%20and%20tech%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20daily%20basis%20our%20rate%20card%20gets%20updated%20on%20our%20application%20as%20per%20market%20rates.%20For%20example%2C%20today%20we%20offer%20Rs%2011%20per%20kg%20of%20rupees%20for%20an%20old%20newspaper%2C%20which%20is%20competitive%20with%20local%20scrap%20dealers%20as%20well.%20In%20this%20business%2C%20accurate%20weight%20is%20far%20more%20important%20than%20higher%20rates.%20We%20always%20use%20well-calibrated%20electronic%20weighing%20scales%20and%20assure%20money%20for%20every%20gram%20to%20the%20customer%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20founders%20explain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETech%2C%20trust%2C%20and%20trackability%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20is%20built%20with%20the%20end-user%20in%20mind.%20Customers%20can%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESchedule%20pickups%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETrack%20waste%20weights%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGet%20digital%20receipts%20and%20payments%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cl